`вҳ… Insight в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`
- The combat system is kept purely functional (no ECS world, no Rapier) вҖ” damage and knockback are computed and returned as values, then applied by the caller with Rapier. This keeps the system fully testable without any game runtime.
- Knockback is computed as a directional impulse vector `(normalized_dir * force)`, not a Rapier impulse directly вҖ” the R3F component translates this to a physics call.
- `invulnFrames` acts as a timer in seconds (decremented by `dt`), not an actual frame counter вҖ” decoupling it from frame rate.
`в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`
